By: Abu ’l-Majdûd b. Âdam Sanâi
---
God is the Self-Existent ... consisting of none but Himself： His acts
and His Essence are beyond instrument and direction, for His Being is above
‘Be’ and ‘He’. ... He is the only Real Existent： all other existences
exist only in the imagination and are subject to His existence.
